Description: FCUK Summer Him?by?FCUK?is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men.?FCUK Summer Him?was launched in 2011. Top notes are bergamot, sea water and nutmeg; middle notes are seaweed, sage, papyrus and lavender; base notes are woodsy notes, teak wood, musk and amber.

Title: Bvlgari Extreme EDC  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: His designer shirt is as flawless as his profile as he shrugs into his dinner jacket and offers his arm to the lady. As he leads her into the restaurant, the power of his luxury fragrance sweeps through her reiterating the effect of his personality and charm on her. The fragrance connoisseurs at Bvlgari designed Extreme to complement the man he is, the potency of his dashing good looks. Heads turn as he strides in and the Eau de Toilette precedes him, announcing his arrival. The deep woody notes of the perfume accentuate the slight ruggedness of his personality blurring the line between handsome and feral. The creator of Bvlgari Extreme plays with the crisp, cool notes to present you with a fragrance the enamours the senses. Warring accords of spicy coriander, herbaceous lavender, galbanum, light tea, juicy grapefruit, neroli, petit grain and zesty bergamot incite the opening notes into dancing flames. The pure heart notes secrete the accords of spice with nutmeg, pepper and cardamom. A slight woodiness colors the heart in the presence of the balsam fir, brazilian rosewood and guaiac wood. As the dry down fades away from your person, accords of iris, sandalwood, oakmoss, cedar and powdery musk make their presence felt, softening the bite of the fragrance. Presented elegantly in a rectangular flacon with simple lines dedicated to minimalism, the slight smoky grey of the fragrance is reflected in the dark depths of his unspeaking eyes. The silver stopper lends elegance, a touch of class to the fragrance. Dance with the devil and live dangerously with Bvlgari Extreme, the fragrance of a man who owns the game.

Title: Rasasi Sahar EDP  -  18 ml(For Men, Women)
Description: Sahar by Rasasi is a finely blended floral woody musk fragrance for women and men. The top notes flow with an oriental and floral theme that is followed by woody, spicy, ambery and rose notes. The fragrance winds up with a balsamic, musky and animalic aroma that stays on for a very long time. Sahar is an enchanting and wonderfully smooth, warm and soft fragrance in concentrated perfume oil form. This exquisite perfume is presented in a solid metal bottle, decorated with feroza crystals and intricate design elements.
